T12TD4278E:105b-42: byed pa po la kta ba tu'o //
T12TD4278E:105b-43: kta ba tu'i 'brel pa grub pa bstan pa las /
T12TD4278E:105b-44: bdag gis bsod nams gang bsgrubs 'gyur //
T12TD4278E:105b-45: de yis 'jig rten 'di mtha' dag / myur du 'jam dbyangs nyid gyur cig /'brel pa grub pa zhes bya ba'i rab tu byed pa slob dpon nyi ma'i snying pos mdzad pa 'di yongs su rdzogs so /
T12TD4278E:105b-47: // / legs par sbyar ba'i skad kyi brda sprod pa'i bstan bcos slob dpon chen po tsandra go mis mdzad pa'i rjes su 'brangs te /
T12TD4278E:105b-48: byed pa can dang tshig sdud dang /
T12TD4278E:105b-50: byings las tshig ting mtha' can sgrub pa dang /
T12TD4278E:105b-51: byings las ming sgrub pa rnams sde tshan du bsgrigs te gsal bar 'chad pa'i bstan bcos nyung zhing rab tu gsal ba pandi ta nyi ma'i snying pos mdzad pa 'di /
T12TD4278E:106a-0: sa thams cad kyi dbang phyug phun sum tshogs pa'i mkhyen rab thugs rje phul du byung ba mnga' ba'i @106a * //
T12TD4278E:106a-1: chos kyi rgyal po chen po spyan snga rin po che dpal ngag gi dbang phyug grags pa phyogs thams cad las rnam par rgyal ba'i lugs gnyis kyi mdun sa chen po pho brang sne'u gdong rtse'i gtsug lag khang du mthun rkyen rnams legs par stsal nas /
T12TD4278E:106a-2: chos kyi rje sprul sku rin po che zhva dmar cod pan 'dzin pa bzhi pa dang dpal ldan dharmma k'irtti dzny'a na shr'i bha dra'i zhal snga nas legs par bsgyur cig ces pa'i bka' lung gnang ba bzhin /
T12TD4278E:106a-3: brda sprod pa'i bstan bcos chen po dag thos nas cha shas tsam rig pa'i zhva lu'i btsun pa 'gos lo ts'a pa dge slong dharmma p'a la bha dra zhes bgyi bas g-yag sde lo ts'a ba'i phyag dpe las gsar du bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o //
T12TD4278E:106a-4: gzhung 'dir ma 'gyur ba dang log par bsgyur //
T12TD4278E:106a-5: ha cang 'gyur sogs dri mar gang gyur pa //
T12TD4278E:106a-6: rgya chan chos spyan dri med mnga' rnams kyis //
T12TD4278E:106a-7: bdag la brtse bas bzod cing bcos par gsol //
T12TD4278E:106a-8: gang gi dpag yas mkhyen brtse'i rnam rol gyis //
T12TD4278E:106a-9: gzhung bzang bsgyur ba'i shing rta bskul ba dang //
T12TD4278E:106a-10: bdag gis bsgyur ba la legs spyad gang thob des //
T12TD4278E:106a-11: mtha' yas mkha' khyab pa 'gro ba'i tshogs kun gyis //
T12TD4278E:106a-12: rang rang skad kyis brjod med don rtogs te //
T12TD4278E:106a-13: dpal ldan chos kyi dung dang gand'i dang //
T12TD4278E:106a-14: zab yang sgra sgrogs chos kyi rnga bo che //
T12TD4278E:106a-15: sgrogs mkhas ngag dbang go 'phang myur thob shog //
T12TD4278E:106a-16: slar yang rgya dpe rnying pa la gtugs te 'gyur bcos dang zhus dang cung zad grub bo//
